graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        DSPO[DSPO Controller]
        DSPO_Health[Health/Metrics<br/>8080-8081/TCP]
        DSPO -->|manages| DSPO_Health
    end

    subgraph "DSPA Instance Components (per namespace)"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent]
        ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
        WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>Argo Workflows]

        MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>Optional]
        Minio[Minio<br/>9000/TCP<br/>Optional]
        MLMD_gRPC[ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP<br/>Optional]
        MLMD_Envoy[ML Metadata Envoy<br/>9090/TCP HTTP<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Optional]
        UI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>3000/TCP<br/>Optional/Unsupported]

        PersistenceAgent -->|syncs state| APIServer
        ScheduledWF -->|creates workflows| WorkflowController
        APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
        APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
        WorkflowController -->|creates| WorkflowPods[Workflow Pods]
        WorkflowPods -->|stores artifacts| Minio
        WorkflowPods -->|tracks lineage| MLMD_gRPC
        MLMD_Envoy -->|proxies| MLMD_gRPC
        UI -->|queries| APIServer
        UI -->|retrieves artifacts| Minio
    end

    User[User/Notebook] -->|creates| DSPA_CR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPA_CR -->|watched by| DSPO
    DSPO -->|deploys| APIServer
    DSPO -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    DSPO -->|deploys| ScheduledWF
    DSPO -->|deploys| WorkflowController
    DSPO -->|deploys| MariaDB
    DSPO -->|deploys| Minio
    DSPO -->|deploys| MLMD_gRPC
    DSPO -->|deploys| MLMD_Envoy
    DSPO -->|deploys| UI

    User -->|submits pipeline| APIServer

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        ArgoWF[Argo Workflows CRDs]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
        ExternalS3[External S3]
        ExternalDB[External Database]
    end

    WorkflowController -->|uses| ArgoWF
    DSPO -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    WorkflowController -->|manages pods| K8sAPI
    APIServer -.->|alternative| ExternalS3
    APIServer -.->|alternative| ExternalDB

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integration"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        Notebooks[ODH Notebooks]
    end

    Dashboard -->|displays runs| APIServer
    Notebooks -->|submits pipelines| APIServer

